le/1/crossheading/the-social-security-act-1993-c3"> The Social Security Act 1993 (c.3)</a></p><ol><li class="LegContentsEntry"><p class="LegContentsItem LegClearFix"><span class="LegDS LegContentsNo"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/58">58.</a></span><span class="LegDS LegContentsTitle"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/58">In section 2(4)(b) of the Social Security Act 1993, for...</a></span></p></li></ol></li><li class="LegClearFix LegContentsPblock"><p class="LegContentsTitle"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/crossheading/the-education-act-1993-c35"> The Education Act 1993 (c.35)</a></p><ol><li class="LegContentsEntry"><p class="LegContentsItem LegClearFix"><span class="LegDS LegContentsNo"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/59">59.</a></span><span class="LegDS LegContentsTitle"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/59">. . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . . .</a></span></p></li></ol></li><li class="LegClearFix LegContentsPblock"><p class="LegContentsTitle"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/crossheading/the-railways-act-1993-c43"> The Railways Act 1993 (c.43)</a></p><ol><li class="LegContentsEntry"><p class="LegContentsItem LegClearFix"><span class="LegDS LegContentsNo"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/60">60.</a></span><span class="LegDS LegContentsTitle"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/60">(1) The Railways Act 1993 is amended as follows. </a></span></p></li></ol></li><li class="LegClearFix LegContentsPblock"><p class="LegContentsTitle"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/crossheading/the-pension-schemes-act-1993-c48"> The Pension Schemes Act 1993 (c.48)</a></p><ol><li class="LegContentsEntry"><p class="LegContentsItem LegClearFix"><span class="LegDS LegContentsNo"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/61">61.</a></span><span class="LegDS LegContentsTitle"><a href="/ukpga/1996/18/schedule/1/paragraph/61">(1) The Pension Schemes Act 1993 is amended as follows....</a></